snippet: Julia Mancuso won a super-G on Sunday in Garmisch-Partenkirchen, Germany, for her first World Cup victory of the season, while her fellow American Lindsey Vonn skied off the course and did not finish.
abstract: American skier Julia Mancuso wins the super-G in Garmisch-Partenkirchen, Germany, for her first World Cup victory of the season; other winter sports results noted.
lead_paragraph: Julia Mancuso won a super-G on Sunday in Garmisch-Partenkirchen, Germany, for her first World Cup victory of the season, while her fellow American Lindsey Vonn skied off the course and did not finish.
